## Repository Structure

```
taod_vega/
├── configs/
│   ├── model_config.yaml       YOLOv8n + TinyBERT hyperparameters
│   ├── fpga_config.yaml        FPGA resource targets
│   └── tasks_config.yaml       14-task benchmark definitions
├── data/
│   ├── download_coco.py        COCO 2017 val downloader
│   └── task_annotations.json  14-task ↔ COCO category mapping
├── stage1_detector/
│   ├── yolov8_detector.py      YOLOv8n wrapper (320×320, INT8)
│   ├── quantize_int8.py        ONNX INT8 post-training quantisation
│   └── nms_postprocess.py      Pure-NumPy + fixed-point NMS
├── stage2_scorer/
│   ├── dual_encoder.py         TinyBERT dual-encoder + alpha scoring
│   ├── custom_transformer.py   Lightweight 2-layer transformer (<2M params)
│   ├── relevance_score.py      Alpha-weighted score fusion utilities
│   └── train_scorer.py         Fine-tuning on 14-task dataset
├── stage3_selector/
│   └── ranked_selector.py      Top-1 selection with threshold
├── pipeline/
│   ├── taod_pipeline.py        End-to-end 3-stage pipeline
│   ├── benchmark.py            14-task COCO accuracy benchmark
│   └── latency_profiler.py     Per-stage latency + throughput
├── fpga/
│   ├── rtl/                    Synthesisable Verilog (Vivado 2023.x)
│   │   ├── cnna_top.v          CNNA top-level
│   │   ├── systolic_array.v    16×16 INT8 MAC systolic array
│   │   ├── weight_buffer.v     512 KB BRAM weight cache
│   │   ├── activation_buffer.v 256 KB double-buffer SRAM
│   │   ├── axi4_dma.v          AXI4 burst DMA engine
│   │   ├── csr_regbank.v       AXI4-Lite CSR register bank
│   │   └── relu_batchnorm.v    Fused ReLU + BN
│   ├── tb/                     Testbenches (VCD → GTKWave)
│   ├── constraints/            XDC timing/IO constraints
│   └── scripts/                Vivado synthesis + impl TCL
├── vega_sw/baremetal/          RISC-V C firmware (no stdlib)
│   ├── main.c                  Boot entry point
│   ├── cnna_driver.{c,h}       CSR register driver
│   ├── yolov8_runtime.c        Layer dispatch to CNNA
│   ├── nms_fixed.c             Q8.8 fixed-point NMS
│   └── tinybert_runtime.c      INT8 TinyBERT inference
├── demo/
│   ├── app.py                  Gradio web demo
│   ├── cli_demo.py             Command-line interface
│   └── visualize_output.py     Bounding box overlay
└── tests/                      Pytest suite (5 integration tests)
```

