## Hardware Deployment

### FPGA Synthesis (Vivado 2023.x)

```tcl
# In Vivado Tcl Console or batch mode:
source fpga/scripts/vivado_synth.tcl
source fpga/scripts/vivado_impl.tcl
```

Target utilisation on XC7K325T:

| Resource | Target | Notes |
|----------|--------|-------|
| LUT | < 70% | 16×16 systolic array |
| DSP48 | < 80% | INT8 MAC units |
| BRAM | < 75% | 512 KB weight + 256 KB activation |
| Fmax | ≥ 100 MHz | 10 ns clock period |

### VEGA Firmware

```bash
cd vega_sw/
make all          # Cross-compile with riscv32-unknown-elf-gcc
make disasm       # Generate .asm listing
make simulate     # Spike ISA simulator
make flash        # JTAG programming via OpenOCD
```

